svg.title: System Sequence Diagram (SSD) - US03 - Add a City

g.text: System Sequence Diagram (SSD) - US03 - Add a City
1. Request to add a city to the map
2.1 Check if a map is currently selected
3.1 Ask for city name, position (X,Y), and house block assignment mode
3.2 Provide city name, position (X,Y), and select assignment mode
[Invalid city name (AC1: A city name cannot have special characters or digits)]
[City name already exists (AC3: When a city name already exists in the map, the system must display a warning to the editor)]
4.1.3 Check if city name already exists
[Manual house block assignment (AC2: The house blocks can be assigned manually or automatically)]
4.4 Automatically assign house blocks based on city position
5. Add city with house blocks to the selected map
